item.title: Problem please help
item.dc:creator: @Jaxus Jaxus
item.description:
@Jaxus wrote:

You need to provide more information about your client:

[ul][li]How does the client obtain the cache? (Directly packed into a folder or automatically downloaded on startup)[/li]
[li]Is anything different with your client compared to everyone else’s?[/li][/ul]

I’m going to go ahead and suggest that it’s possibly a sprite problem, and this can either lead to the sprite simply not being in the cache or a bad directory to the sprite.
